St. Martin's Episcopal Church (640 Hawthorn Lane) is the location of the Davis Community Meals, which serves free meals to homeless and low income individuals and families on Tuesday nights from 5:45 to 6:30 and on Saturdays from 11:30 a.m. to 12:15 p.m., on a walk-in basis.  

Volunteers are always needed for food prep, cooking, serving, and cleanup.

Call:  530 756-4008 to volunteer.
